# React Dashboard Conventions

- Functional components only, no class components
- All component props must have TypeScript interfaces
- Use Tailwind utility classes exclusively, no inline styles or CSS modules
- Import event types from shared/event_schema.ts
- WebSocket messages are always CrossfireEvent JSON
- Color tokens via CSS variables: --color-clean, --color-critical, --color-warning, --color-info
- Font: JetBrains Mono for all monospace/code text
- Use lucide-react for icons
- @xyflow/react for flow graph (not old reactflow package)
- All WebSocket communication goes through the useWebSocket hook
